<plot>Since the triumphs of the civil rights legislations of the early 1960's havoc and decimation has been wreaked on the Black family with a specific devastation on the Black man. With myths and stereotypes of the media, the failed policy of the great society and modern era black leadership abandoning tenants that held the community together during slavery, a new form of mental slavery has perpetuated an undeclared civil war in the Black Community.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?651499</url></doc>
